g: Abstract   Grand Rapids Generating Station Canada is located at Grand Rapids, Manitoba, Canada. Location coordinates are: Latitude= 53.16025, Longitude= -99.28705. This infrastructure is of TYPE Hydro Power Plant with a design capacity of 472 MWe. It has 4 unit(s). The first unit was commissioned in 1965 and the last in 1968. It is operated by Manitoba Hydro.
